Package: llmshieldr
Title: Safety Guardrails for LLM Workflows in R
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A model-agnostic safety layer for R developers building with
    large language models. Covers all ten OWASP LLM Top 10 (2025) risk
    categories via a composable rule engine. Supports regex rules, lightweight
    NLP intent checks, and semantic (LLM-reviewer) checks on prompts, retrieved
    context, and model outputs. Supports local Ollama workflows via ellmer
    and works with other R-callable chat interfaces.
    Suitable for all industries.
